text:
We are having some issues i'm hoping someone else might have run in to before as we are not able to find documentation around this.

We had uploaded a brand new dar file with new templates to DevNet. Making calls through grpc to the ledger results in the error below:

```Servlet.service() for servlet [dispatcherServlet] in context with path [] threw exception [Request processing failed: java.util.concurrent.CompletionException: io.grpc.StatusRuntimeException: FAILED_PRECONDITION: NO_DOMAIN_FOR_SUBMISSION(9,0d3d024c): No valid domain for submission found.] with root cause```
Based on some other forums we confirmed that the new DAR was vetted which seemed to be a previous problem.

If anyone knows of a resource to point us to or run in to this in the past, any help would be appreciated!
